data.description: Welcome to your Luxe Sanctuary! This magnificent home boasts over 1,700 sq ft of meticulously crafted living space, totaling 2,544 sq ft.  Nestled on over 1/4 acre corner lot within a quiet and enjoyable community makes this home an enjoyable oasis!  Indulge in the embrace of three luxury size bedrooms, one of which can be designated as your exclusive guest wing.  Your new home exudes distinction full of upgrades such as hurricane impact windows throughout, new stainless steel appliance package, cozy fireplace and much more!  Experience the grandeur of a chef's inspired kitchen!  As the Florida winter breeze sweeps through, you'll relish the refreshing coolness while unwinding on your expanded, screened lanai. Make it yours today!
